title: Bob Marley & The Wailers - Live Studio Recordings Intro to the M
description:
Product Description
Japanese Exclusive! Into The Matrix is a 12-track CD featuring a previously unreleased studio jam recorded prior to the concerts at the Matrix, San Francisco in 1973 with guest appearances by Peter Tosh, Joe Higgs, Earl Lindo and more.

2. Slave Driver
3. Burnin&#039; And Lootin&#039;
4. Rastaman Chant
5. Duppy Conqueror
6. Midnight Ravers
7. Put It On (Lord I Thank You)
8. Stop That Rain
9. Kinky Reggae
10. Stir It Up
11. No More Trouble
12. Get Up, Stand Up
